2025) 845 final)', 'Opinion of the European Economic and Social Committee – Communication from the Commission to the European Parliament and the Council – EU Defence Industry Transformation Roadmap: Unleashing Disruptive Innovation for Defence Readiness (Optional referral) (COM(2025) 845 final)', 'Opinion of the European Economic and Social Committee – Communication from the Commission to the European Parliament and the Council – EU Defence Industry Transformation Roadmap: Unleashing Disruptive Innovation for Defence Readiness (Optional referral) (COM(2025) 845 final)'], 'observables': {'domain-name': ['europa.eu'], 'url': ['http://data.europa.eu/eli/C/2026/3232/oj', 'https://eur-lex.europa.eu/content/help/eurlex-content/experimental-features.html']}}, {'title': 'OJ:C_202603220: Opinion of the European Economic and Social Committee\xa0– Enhancing quality in employment and working conditions by introducing and promoting related tools (including AI) and strengthening social dialogue and collective bargaining (exploratory opinion requested by the Cypriot presidency)', 'publication_date': 'Thu, 02 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0200', 'source': 'https://eur-lex.europa.eu/./legal-content/AUTO/?uri=OJ:C_202603220', 'source_type': "['']", 'source_level': 2, 'text': ["Do you want to help improving EUR-Lex ? This is a list of experimental features that you can enable. These features are still under development; they are not fully tested, and might reduce EUR-Lex stability. Don't forget to give your feedback!", 'Opinion of the European Economic and Social Committee – Enhancing quality in employment and working conditions by introducing and promoting related tools (including AI) and strengthening social dialogue and collective bargaining (exploratory opinion requested by the Cypriot presidency)', 'Opinion of the European Economic and Social Committee – Enhancing quality in employment and working conditions by introducing and promoting related tools (including AI) and strengthening social dialogue and collective bargaining (exploratory opinion requested by the Cypriot presidency)', 'Opinion of the European Economic and Social Committee – Enhancing quality in employment and working conditions by introducing and promoting related tools (including AI) and strengthening social dialogue and collective bargaining (exploratory opinion requested by the Cypriot presidency)'], 'observables': {'domain-name': ['europa.eu'], 'url': ['http://data.europa.eu/eli/C/2026/3220/oj', 'https://eur-lex.europa.eu/content/help/eurlex-content/experimental-features.html']}}]